snippet.title: Dark Saviour - Sega Saturn - Gameplay
snippet.description: Very much overlooked and underrated RPG on the Saturn with a fantastic so innovative parallel system and also a game that pushed some of the best 3D graphics on the Saturn. The music is also brilliant and all played off the sound chip
